{"tid":1788240,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃色經濟圈] 用美金交易？","createTime":"2019-12-18T13:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T05:48:15.000Z","uid":102108,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb3402667b477adc949b3ad6c14057047c17d503","tid":1788240,"uid":102108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"究竟黃色經濟圈用美金交易有冇用/可唔可行？<br />\n之前就唔少人出糧即刻換美金/拎現金<br />\n但就拎住舊錢冇乜用<br />\n如果黃色經濟圈可以用美金交易 <br />\n咪多咗個誘因令更多人換美金<br />\n理想嘅話將來可以衣食住都可以俾美金？<br />\n有冇好處？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 dse冇讀econ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29348dd410f6c1cc55dcf80680b0c0936ea29a90","tid":1788240,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"你用美金俾，黃店要用返港弊俾供應商，就係晒氣，仲要白蝕買賣差價"},{"pid":"03cf3205b256bf1ce5e9b47d9d3231d81801be82","tid":1788240,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:01:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5d79ca7dba61d29a7fb8b4a87443b829be419965","tid":1788240,"uid":102108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"29348dd410f6c1cc55dcf80680b0c0936ea29a90","tid":1788240,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"你用美金俾，黃店要用返港弊俾供應商，就係晒氣，仲要白蝕買賣差價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"即係成條鏈有一part唔用美金都係晒氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇黃嘅supplier list<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係冇 當係誘因令更多人換美金都好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(其係唔係好記得換美金嘅作用係咩)<br />\n美金係香港流通會唔會有咩